text:
Niall Horan got a huge scare from his One Direction buddy Harry Styles... well someone that was dressed up like Harry.

While on The Ellen DeGeneres Show, Horan was scared as a "Harry Styles" jumped out of the side table on stage. His reaction is so adorable!
title: A Fake Harry Styles Scares Niall Horan On Ellen Show
